overview: Farm hand Brett DiMineo fears losing his job, then discovers a secret door leading him into a different reality of dungeons and leather. Brett watches Bryan Archer and Ty Parks gettin git on, then mixes it up with Kyle Richards and Zane West before freeing captive leather king Trey Rexx in exchange for a promise. Back in the barn, muscleman Mark Dalton whacks himself off in the hayloft before Trey enters and stops loan officer Leo Bramm from foreclosing on the farm... King Leather style.
title: Ranch Hand Muscle
